            <div class="everyonelovesstackoverflow" id="adzerk504904073">
            </div>

            <div class="welovestackoverflow" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
Sharding is a technique of partitioning database tables by row ("horizontally"); typically this technique requires a key to be selected that determines how the rows are to be partitioned.                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/sharding/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
                            <span class="lsep">|</span> 
                            <a title="top answerers and askers in this tag" href="/tags/sharding/topusers">top users</a> 
                            <span class="lsep">|</span> 
                            <a title="common, alternate spellings or phrasings for this tag" href="/tags/sharding/synonyms">synonyms (1)</a>
                                                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

